und:#E4FFFF;}\r\n.shop_title {background-color:#8DF7F7;color:#090909;border-bottom-color:#1ABDE6;border-top-color:#D5FCFB;}\r\n.board_t_shop {border-color:#8DF7F7;}\r\n.board_bg_shop {background:#F9FFFE;}\r\n.topic_title {border-bottom-color:#1ABDE6;}\r\n<\/style>","bgSound":"","clubF_name":"院校","desktop":"","docinfo":[{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_351_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十三，《南京之歌》邓丽君歌曲和林彪叛逃<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七一年夏一天晚上，连队稻场上聚集着一些各地的男女<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">新<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">知青在谈天纳凉。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 屋子里太热，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">呆不住人。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">而屋外四周都是水田，到处都是蚊子，实在没地方可去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 原先在二连王台孜，队部旁边就是高邮湖大堤坝，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">夏日傍晚我们可以上大坝乘凉。大坝上<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">时有湖风徐来，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很凉快，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还可以观赏天光水色。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 而三连在大圹圩中心，四下一望无边的都是水田。要纳凉，只有到稻场。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 好在稻场是水泥的，很干净，还有篮球架。假如是月夜，也有人夜晚<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还在篮球场<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">练习投篮。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">屋<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">子<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">朝西晒，屋子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">里<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">比其他人家更<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">热<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。虽然太阳早已经落山，依然<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">酷暑难耐<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无法入睡，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来到稻场和这些新知青在一起在闲聊。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这时有个上海男知青在稻场旁边<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">忘情地<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">小声唱歌。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 歌词是：啊，南京，我可爱的故乡。啊，南京，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">何时才能回到你的身旁？蓝蓝的天上，白云在飞翔。美丽的扬子江畔，是我可爱的南京古城我的家乡。啊，彩虹般的大桥，直耸云霄，横跨长江。威武的钟山，虎踞在我的家乡……&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当时，我被这首歌忧伤的情感和优美曲调深深地感动了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这个唱歌的上海知青告诉我，这首歌叫《南京之歌》。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当晚，这首《南京之歌》<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">引发了我的思想之情，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我夜不能寐，写一支套曲《知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">岁<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">月》<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 曲曰：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [南吕][一枝花]空怀凌云志，含泪别故园。少小逼种田，下乡上山。四野荒原，搭草棚扎营盘，那管他众男女身娇软。苦劳力春种秋<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">收<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，多少次梦回乡关<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [梁州]饱尝尽凄凉饥寒，度日月困苦艰难，囊中羞有家难还。万里神州，红旗招展，标语口号，铺地盖天。整日介西<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">方<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">苦难，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">傻<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">乎乎忠心赤胆。愁的是大雪纷飞衣尚单，怕的是父老母衰泪涟涟，喜的是赊酒菜故人访探。暗自许愿，憨畅想再返学府院，同窗携手言欢。何时握笔把墨研？能沉浸书案？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [尾]谋稻粱红尘无人问冷暖，豆蔻年华忒难堪。读唐诗怕批封面贴毛选，可怜可叹，三十里乐颠颠走来回把<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">《望乡》<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看。&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当然，此曲不能示人，我只敢将曲子拿给少数铁杆哥们看。倘若被那些极左的军人知道，我必然没好果子吃。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我心想，《南京之歌》如此出名，作者肯定要倒霉。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 后来我得知此歌作者是南京的知青任毅。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 果然，我们很快就听到任毅因写这首歌曲，被当成现行反革命抓捕入狱的不幸消息。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一曲游子怀念亲人故土的歌曲，有的只是乡愁情思，怎么就<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">成<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了反革命了？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那个时代的文字狱<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，由此可见。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在，每当看见一些当年的知青们，在写文著述歌颂“上山下乡”时，我就从心底里就产生厌恶和冷笑：你们说的是真话吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-09 09:20","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-09 09:20:02","ShortDate":"07-09 09:20","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":350,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_352_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有次，我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">专程<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">去<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了一次<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">天长县<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，是去<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看望谷志瑞、龚毅青两口子。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谷志瑞已经恢复<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">工<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">作，担任天长县革委会副主任（主任是军人兼任）。龚毅青也解放了，二人精神状态都很好，但说话<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">皆<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十谨慎。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对此，我自然能理解。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 临行，龚毅青送我一个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上海生产的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">小<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">型熊猫牌<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">半导体无线电收音机<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 广播里整天到晚没完没了的政治宣传<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不爱听，文艺节目就是几个样板戏和那些听腻了的革命歌曲，因此，我非常喜爱这个收音机。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这台“熊猫”牌袖珍无线电收音机功能很强大，在当<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">时<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是很高档的奢侈<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">商<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">品。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这台收音机<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">可<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">以清晰地收听到台湾的“自由中国之声”、苏联<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">塔斯社<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的“莫斯科广播电台”和美国的“美国之音”等“敌台”广播。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 政治恐怖，无处不在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">收听“敌台”广播，就是现行反革命行为。因此我在摆弄这个收音机和调台的时候，非常谨慎。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 记得<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我在王台孜的时候，有个同乡<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老知青，他的耳朵有点背，有次他在调试收音机的时候，无意中碰到了敌台。因为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">啊<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">耳聋听不清楚，就将音量放大听，一听是敌台，吓得他连忙将收音机关掉。可惜，已经迟了，被人听见了。结果，他被打成了“偷听敌台”的反革命。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我当然不敢公开听“敌台”，若被人听见，那还得了？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 因为当时没有耳机，我只能悄悄躲在没有人的远处野外，或在自己的被窝里收听。既受罪，又担惊受怕，很不是滋味。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有次夜晚，我在摆弄收音机的时候，听到了台湾的“自由中国之声”播放的邓丽君的《难忘初恋的情人》这首歌。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这是我第一次听到邓丽君演唱的歌曲。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 邓丽君甜美的嗓音，自然清纯的演唱风格深深感染、吸引了我。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在听惯了众多歇斯底里的歌曲后，邓丽君的歌曲<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">朴实无华而情感真挚，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">像是荒漠里的一股清泉，深深滋润了我孤独寂寞的心田。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从此，我迷上了邓丽君的歌曲，一直到现在依然喜欢听。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可是，这台收音机很费电池，两天不到，四节电池就耗光了，我实在消费不起。加之我知道这东西是个隐患，常在河边转，难免不湿脚。即使我听“敌台”别人没抓住把柄，只要是有人怀疑我偷听敌台，那也是很危险的事情。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 于是，这个收音机我玩了一个月后，我又去天长，忍痛割爱，将这台收音机还给了龚毅青。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-09 09:25","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-09 09:25:10","ShortDate":"07-09 09:25","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":351,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_353_0\"><img src=\"http://imgs.xici.net/_img/emot/panda/3.gif\" />施恩不图报<div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u20916672/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-09 16:14","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-09 16:14:46","ShortDate":"07-09 16:14","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u20916672.htm","UserID":20916672,"UserName":"周家小五","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":352,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_354_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 国庆节后，我听说岳中林的大女儿岳丽华考上了中国科技大学，我为她、为她全家感到高兴。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由于我和她全家人都可以算是患难之交，因此她一家人都和我相处得<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很好。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 自岳中林担任副团长后，我就很少到他家去，个中情由，心照不宣。岳中林的夫人朱艺芳<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">时已经从怀远龙亢农场调到了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">天长县<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大圹圩<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">农场<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。为此，朱艺芳只要看见我就<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">数<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">落我，说我与她家走动的少了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳丽华考上了中国科技大学<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">应<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">该<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">到她家<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祝贺一下。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">于是我抽空来到场部，探望岳中林一家人。我在他家吃了一顿中饭，说了说连队下面的事情。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 饭后，岳中林将我喊进他卧室，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要和我单独谈<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谈话<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 自从认识<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">岳中林<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，他和我说话，从来没有回避过他家的任何人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 今天他却要避开他家的亲人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">跟我单独谈话，让我十分纳闷。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来到岳中林卧室，岳中林关上门，严肃地着我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他要我坐在椅子上，他自己则<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">坐在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">床沿<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上半天没开口。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在自己<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">家里<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的卧室里和我谈话<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为什么<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要关门？<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我坐在椅子上惊奇地看着他，不知道发生了什么大事。但我心里清楚，一定是发生什么大事了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 半响，岳中林才小声严肃地对我说：“林彪死了！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 啊！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我大吃一惊。问：“林彪死了？怎么死的？”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林凝重地点点头说：“叛逃，飞机失事，摔死在外蒙。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我愣住了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我自然知道岳中林的消息必然来自官方。于是便问林彪为什么要叛逃？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林告诉我，中央文件说林彪要谋害毛主席，被毛主席察觉，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">九月十三日夜晚，林彪<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">全家坐飞机<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">企图<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">逃跑<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">到苏联<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，结果飞机在外蒙失事。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中央将此事定名为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“九一三事件”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我愣了一会，方问：“摔死了？摔死的？”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林点点头。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我用“不可思议”和“难以服人”几个字，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">向岳中林<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">表现出对此说的怀疑。&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林没有批评我对中央文件的怀疑，他只是严肃地说，这是中央绝密文件，才传达到县团级<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">去<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">省会<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">合肥听<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">传达<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">昨天才回来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我的头脑在飞速思考：林彪是毛泽东法定接班人，他为什么要叛逃？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林叮嘱我说，这件事情你不要对你的那些朋友<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说，千万不能告诉任何人。今晚团党委要将文件传达到<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">营<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">以上干部，明天<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">传达到连一级干部，后天<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">各连传达到党员干部，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">后天传达到党员，然后再传达到群众。上级有严格规定，谁泄密就以党纪国法论处谁。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我点点头。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 岳中林当然是知道我做事稳妥，才将这件机密大事告诉我。也许他是想知道我这样身在社会底层的人，对此事的反应。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 告别岳中林，我在回三连的路上，一直在思考这件惊天大事。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 直觉告诉我，林彪的死，必将敲碎神坛上被人供奉的毛泽东这尊神像。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一个国家战功卓著的军队元帅、法定的党主席接班人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">却叛党背国了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无论是什么原因，对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">毛泽东<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，对中国，都是一件无法自圆其说的政治大丑闻。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我对林彪的意外死亡，虽然很震惊，说实话，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也很钦佩，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也有些幸灾乐祸。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一路无人，我纵情唱起台湾歌曲《往事难追回》：莫为春梦空陶醉，春梦一去难追回。不要陶醉<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">春<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">梦美，醒来梦已碎。夜幕又轻轻低垂，我不想和你梦中相依偎。只因为春梦虽<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">好<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，只能回味，只能回味，住事难追回……<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-09 17:47","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-09 17:47:21","ShortDate":"07-09 17:47","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":353,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_355_0\"><b style=\"color:#3366ee;\">回复 第354楼 的 @半醉汉：<\/b><br />\r\n<div><b style=\"color:rgb(51, 102, 238);\"><font face=\"黑体\" size=\"5\">心情不错！<\/font><\/b><\/div><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u20360133/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-09 20:07","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-09 20:07:08","Sh