font-size:18pt;\">说林彪<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">长得是獐头鼠目。还说林彪这个名字更不好，是林中窜出一只虎，回马杀三刀。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">事涉攻击、侮辱林副统帅的政治大事，被人告发。听<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说此人已经被抓，即将重判。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 假如传闻是真的，我不知道这位拆字先生的命运会是什么样。是重判他？还是无罪释放？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在，按官方说法，林彪因<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要谋害毛主席，阴谋败露，仓皇出逃，死于非命。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 真有趣啊。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 回到家，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">首先映入<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">眼帘<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我办公桌上放着<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一本最新的解放军画报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我不由哑然失笑。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 因为这张画报的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">整个<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">封面，正是林彪的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一张大大的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">头像。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">照片上，林副统帅手里拿着毛主席著作在认真看，他身着军装，光着头，学习得很认真。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最具讽刺意味的是，这张照片的拍摄者，正是毛泽东的夫人，中央文革小组组长江青同志。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 真是莫大的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">笑话<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 尽管岳中林叮嘱我，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">林彪叛逃<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这件事千万不要对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">朋友们说，但我还是按捺不住兴奋，当天晚上，我还是将这一重大消息悄悄告诉了裔师傅和周颂平。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当然我也叮嘱了他们，事涉岳中林的政治前途和我的安危，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">你们自己知道就行了，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谁也不要<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">再向别人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">泄密。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 裔师傅听罢长叹，连叹中国的事情真没有意思，说是人民当家作主，实际上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无论<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">什么事情<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是严严实实地<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">把我们老百姓蒙在鼓里。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周颂平则连连摇头，叹息政治黑暗，宫廷肮脏，长吟“周公恐惧流言日，王莽谦恭未篡时。向使当初身便死，一生真伪复谁知？”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们都清楚，毛泽东不会在林彪事件上承认自己的失误、错误，只会掩盖自己，将一切责任推给<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">林彪或<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">别人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">按惯例，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一场新的政治运动<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很快就会<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来临，毛泽东会千方百计将林彪说成<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他原来就<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">个大坏蛋。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可是，怎么能将一个亲密的战友、自己的法定<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">接班人，几十年转战南北的开国元帅，说成是一个十恶不赦的阶级敌人而能让人深信不疑，在毛泽东面前是个大难题。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 无论么说，林彪事件，使毛泽东在人们的心里，再也伟大、正确不起来了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 稍微有点独立思考能力的人，谁都会在心里发出疑问：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不说远的，仅仅这几年，就<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">前有彭德怀、刘少奇，后有陈伯达，如今又出来个林彪，怎么都是老牌共产党<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">反对你毛泽东呢？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有一位老友一针见血地说：你明察秋毫，你高瞻远瞩，你无往不胜，你洞察一切，哦，结果你自己还被你的好学生糊弄了几十年。你难倒是个傻子？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-10 10:11","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-10 10:11:37","ShortDate":"07-10 10:11","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":357,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_359_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第358楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" size=\"4\">稍微有点独立思考能力的人，谁都会在心里发出疑问...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<font size=\"5\">我说什么就是什么,只有我说的,没有你们想的.<\/font><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-10 20:01","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-10 20:01:12","ShortDate":"07-10 20:01","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":358,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_360_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连队在传达“九一三事件”的时候，也是先<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">将中央文件传达到<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">党员<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和副连长、排长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">第二天再传达到<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">群众。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会场<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">安排在稻场旁边的大仓库里，大仓库<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">前后左右，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">如临大敌，煞有介事地<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">均设有岗哨<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那些正在被专政的“反革命分子”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">坏分子<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，则不准听这个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">中央<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文件。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在听传达中央文件的时候，我们知道了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在林彪的众多罪行中，有一个“五七一工程纪要”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据说，这个“五七一”是“武起义”的谐音。说<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">林彪要“武<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">装<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">起义”，要干掉毛主席。可<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">中央<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文件里，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有关林彪要谋杀毛泽东的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">具体事实，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">即使在林彪<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">死后<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">死无对证的情况下，依然拿不出丝毫直接<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">证据，全是牵强附会。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">让人不得不怀疑<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">安在林彪头上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这个罪名<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">真<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">假<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">？<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这份材料上有句林彪说的话，是“知识青年上山下乡，等于变相劳改”，真是说到很多知识青年的心窝子里去了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">事件给我们这代人带来心理上的巨大冲击<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，迫使人们去思考：这到底为什么？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这个事件对社会最大的贡献，就是打破了神坛上毛泽东的神圣、权威形象，人们开始在内心怀疑他的革命动机了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一位上海女知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">曾<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">私下遗憾而惋惜地对我说，林彪的“知识青年上山下乡，等于变相劳改”这句话说得太好了，看起来真是好人不长寿，恶魔活千年！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 真是爱憎分明，立场坚定，掷地有声。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 历史学家<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">刘小萌<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">《中国知青史．大潮》<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">中说：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“尤其是年轻的一代，他们首先感到的是自己对领袖的赤诚之心和圣洁之情受到了亵渎，认为自己上了当，受了骗。当他们因受骗而备受煎熬时，当他们因失去理想主义的精神支柱而四顾彷徨时，一种近乎绝望的心理往往攫住了他们的心。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此段语言，是痛心疾首的中肯之论。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪叛逃<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">事件<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">保密一个月后，中央有关<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">才在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">全国下达<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过前期的舆论准备，报纸<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">由一贯歌颂林彪，现在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">开始<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">转向<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">批判林彪了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 好笑的是，批判林彪，林彪的名字却不能在报纸上出现。掩耳盗铃已成习惯，报纸上称林彪为“刘少奇一类骗子”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 全中国人都知道<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，以前报纸上说的“中国的赫鲁晓夫”是指刘少奇，现在报纸上说的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“刘少奇一类骗子”就是指林彪<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">可报纸就是羞答答不好意思直接说。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 犹抱琵琶半遮面的若是个少女很好看，若是个涂脂抹粉的大老爷们，你说那给人会是什么感觉？若是媒体报纸也犹抱琵琶半遮面，算什么？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “九一三事件”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文件传达后，有天<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">罗指导员交给我一个额外的政治任务，叫我写<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">篇批判林彪的文章，一定要争取在安徽省建设兵团办的《兵团战士》报上发表。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我硬着头皮答应下来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可是我又不了解林彪，我能批判他什么呢？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在我以前接触过的报纸、文件、书籍、传说，所有林彪的事迹中，全部都是肯定、夸奖、表扬、赞扬、歌颂他的文字。现在叫我写文章批判林彪，我实在为难。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 任务必须完成。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 无奈之下，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我翻出两首林彪写的词《西江月．重上井冈山》，做起文章。尽管我怀疑林彪这两首词，可能是有人捉刀而为。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这两首词，一<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">首<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 繁茂三湾竹树，苍茫五哨云烟，井冈搏斗忆当年，唤起人间巨变。红日光弥宇宙，战旗涌作重洋，工农亿万志昂扬，誓把敌顽埋葬。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 第<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">二<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">首<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是：<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;四十年前旧地，万千往事萦怀，英雄烈士启蒿莱，生死艰难度外。志壮坚信马列，岂疑星火燎原，辉煌胜利共开颜，斗<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">志<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不容稍减。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我知道<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">林<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">彪大革命时在井冈山，曾质疑<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">过革命的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“红旗到底能打多久”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就利用词中“岂疑星火燎原”这句，上纲上线一番，说他在井冈山就怀疑“红旗到底能打多久”，对革命前途悲观失望。而现在在词中又说“岂疑星火燎原”，就是出尔反尔，是公然反对毛主席当时对他的批评。我利用词中“井冈搏斗忆当年，唤起人间巨变”这句，说他是将自己美化成井冈山红军的代表，贪天功为己有，与毛主席争辉。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 东拼西凑<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无限上纲，强词夺理，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">聊以交差。&nbsp; <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 稿子寄到省<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">《兵团战士》报<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">居然<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">立即<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">给刊登出来了。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 惭愧，我的一篇言不由衷的文章，就这样由草稿，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">第一次<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">变成了报纸上的铅字。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 好歹，我算完成罗指导员交给我的任务了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他看见我们连<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">写<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的文章上了《兵团战士》报，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">非常<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">高兴。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文章在省一级的报纸上发表<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，一些新来的知青，都对我很崇拜。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我有自知之明，我苦笑。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-10 21:43","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-10 21:43:28","ShortDate":"07-10 21:43","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":359,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_361_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 批判“刘少奇一类骗子”，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当然也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要在现实中找<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">阶级斗争活靶子打<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">只有<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这样<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">才能印证毛主席有关阶级斗争理论的正确。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">才能震慑与领导离心离德的落后分子和一些“别有用心”的人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 党支部发动积极分子，满连队找“刘少奇一类骗子”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在基层的代言人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">活靶子。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 人人谨小慎微，说话都很注意，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谁也不愿意<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、不敢<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">乱说<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">话。能当阶级斗争活靶子打的人，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">找起来其实也不容易。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有话不说的人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，谁也不<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">能<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出卖<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。敢说话的人，都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在铁哥们小范围内说，没人告密。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一时半时<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">连队<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">找不到<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">合适的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人当这个阶级斗争的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">活靶子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员有点着急。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这时，一个傻乎乎姓刘的老知青碰在了枪口上。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">干活<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">休息时<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">心血来潮，说起儿时旧事<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他说他小的时候，村子里来了一队日本鬼子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这些日本鬼子对人很和气，尤其喜欢小孩，还发小糖给孩子吃<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，因此<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">村子里的孩子们都很喜欢日本鬼子。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他还说他第一次吃小糖，吃的就是日本鬼子给他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">吃<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">日本<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">小糖。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 平心而论，他这样说并不是为了美化日本侵略者，他说的只是他小时候的偶然所见<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，也有种卖弄自己见过日本人的意思。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这就祸从口出了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有个积极分子就将他的话汇报<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">给<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">党支部<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">罗指导员<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员听罢大怒，啊！居然敢说日本鬼子对我们中国人很和气！敢说我们中国的孩子们都很喜欢日本鬼子！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这样的人不斗，斗谁？<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我想，罗指导员也大喜，因为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们连<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">终于有了一个“刘少奇一类骗子”的活靶子可<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">以大<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">打<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">特打<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连队先是在我们本连开斗争会，斗这个姓刘的老知青。后在团宣传股觉得我们连这个斗争会效果好，被树为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">联系实际批判<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“刘少奇一类骗子”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">典型，在全团巡回<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">批斗<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员叫我带队，与<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老知青<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">周颂平、李永光、一个上海女知青，外加这个被斗的姓刘的老知青，我们五个人坐着驴车到各连队巡回批斗他，脱产干革命。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 路上还是周<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">颂<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">平赶驴车。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 姓刘的老知青也被斗油条了，他在批斗会上，做出种种自我批判的检查，言不由衷地说自己是如何如何美化日本侵略者，说自己是汉奸。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们则对他上纲上线，严加批判。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我是文书，周颂平是赶驴车的，我俩不要下地干活，李永光、上海女知青和姓刘的老知青，因为抓革命，就不要干又累又苦的农活了，故而斗人的和被斗的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都很乐意。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 批斗会后，其它连会热情招待我们吃一顿免费的午餐。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 台上分敌友，台下是难友。我们也不能让姓刘的老知青饿着，大家在一起吃。然后我们一起坐驴车，一路说<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">笑笑再回来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三连联系实际批判“刘少奇一类骗子”的活动，取得良好成效。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 姓刘的老知青开始的时候畏惧批斗<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">后来被斗的次数多了，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不怕了，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">起先<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还有些羞涩。最后就习惯、麻木、无所谓了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 人被迫害折磨至此，这个社会环境邪恶的程度要有多深？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 秋收大忙<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">季节，这位姓刘的老知青还特别怀念他被巡回批斗的那些日子。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有时候<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他会在无人之际<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">找机会主动向我打听：“文书，我这几天干活累死了，什么时候再带我出去给你们批斗几天啊？”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 若<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">发言批判别人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">李永光<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，或是那个<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上海女知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">觉得干活劳累，是他们提出来再搞一次巡回批斗会，还可以理解。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">现在，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是挨斗的人自己主动提出来开巡回斗争会斗争他，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这更让人感到悲哀和寒心。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这也证明，脑力劳动比体力劳动<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">轻松<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">愉快<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">得多。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当时<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我也很同情他的劳累<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有一天，我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">向罗指导员<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">建<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">议，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">巡回批斗会效果很好，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是不是再联系一个我们大批判组没去过的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">连队，再<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">斗一斗我们连<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“刘少奇一类骗子”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的活靶子？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员善如流，基本<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">听从我的意见。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 李永光和<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">那个上海女知青<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，以及<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">被批斗的姓刘的老知青<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">知道第二天要进行巡回批斗时，因为不要干活了，俱都十分高兴。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 斗人的和被斗的如此和谐，你见过吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-10 22:58","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-10 22:58:12","ShortDate":"07-10 22:58","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":360,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_362_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第361楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">斗人的和被斗的如此和谐，你见过吗？...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<font face=\"黑体\" size=\"5\">说明这种批斗形式符合民意，深得人心。<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u20360133/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-11 08:17","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-11 08:17:02","ShortDate":"07-11 08:17","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u20360133.htm","UserID":20360133,"Us