要的油、盐、酱、醋、烟、酒等日用品，则是理发店<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">寿县<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的老知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">孙某<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">代卖。他也提出不能再兼顾，要么专门理发，要么专门开小店。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连部经过考虑，决定办个代销店，专卖日用品和粮油。既能方便群众，也减轻了保管员、理发员的工作压力。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最后，连部决定由小杨当专职营业员<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这个小店就办在我家。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 营<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">业员就不要下地干活了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连部这样安排，也有照顾我的意思。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当然，这也<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是连队领导对我的工作比较满意<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的一种表示<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-11 19:06","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-11 19:06:50","ShortDate":"07-11 19:06","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":368,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_370_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十五，陈毅追悼会和龙卷风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">报纸<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">刊登的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">毛泽东照片<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上，我们都能看到毛泽东<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在迅速衰老<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的形象<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">光辉，只剩下<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无精打采<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪事件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大大挫伤了毛泽东<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的锐气，大大损伤了他的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">元气。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 也难怪，中国有十大元帅，个个出类拔萃，但毛泽东独独钟爱林彪。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪对此，自有回报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九六六年十二月十六日，林彪在《毛主席语录再版前言》中说：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “毛泽东同志是当代最伟大的马克思列宁主义者。毛泽东同志天才地、创造性地、全面地继承、捍卫和发展了马克思列宁主义，把马克思列宁主义提高到一个崭新的阶段。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪对毛泽东极尽拍马奉承，有目共睹。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当然，我们不排除这是林彪有意迷惑毛泽东，而故作的溢美之词，是一种策略。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九六七年五月一日是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">劳动节<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，林彪为《人民日报》题词：伟大的导师、伟大的领袖、伟大的统帅、伟大的舵手，毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 题词的手迹发表在当日《人日报》第一版毛主席像下面。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五月二日《人民日报》头<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">版<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">头条称：“我们的副统帅林彪同志为今年‘五一’国际劳动节的题词，最集中的表达出了亿万人民对毛主席无限热爱、无限忠诚、无限信仰、无限崇拜的感情，成为今天整个节日庆祝活动中最响亮的颂歌。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪的“四个伟大”，再加上《人民日报》的“四个无限”，曲意迎奉至此境界，令<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有心<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人侧目<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">叹息<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 然毛泽东是欣欣然笑纳。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那些失宠的、被冷落的老帅们对此，自然会鄙视林彪。现在林彪死了，他们在讥讽、同情之余，焉能不看毛泽东的笑话？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 毛泽东受此挫折，必然会想到这些和自己一起举旗造反的那些老弟<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">兄<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们。他们比起林彪，其实更可靠。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七二年一月六日，陈毅逝世，终年七十一岁。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中央军委决定一月十日为陈毅召开追悼会。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 陈毅当时的官方头衔，是中共中央委员、中央军委副主席、国务院副总理兼外交部长、政协<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">副<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">主席<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">国防委员会副主席、中华人民共和国元帅。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但事实上，陈毅和<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">朱德等<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这批开国元勋<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老帅<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，早已被毛泽东打入冷宫，失去权力，甚至被剥夺了工作权利。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 陈毅逝世，按照当时的规定，他已经不算<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">党和国家<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">领导人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 追悼会由中央军委出面组织，总政治部主任李德生主持追悼会，军委副主席叶剑英致悼词，政治局委员不一定<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出席。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但一月十日，身穿睡衣的毛泽东突然作出决定，要去参加陈毅的追悼会。老人家连换装，整容修饰等程序都免了，值班卫士只好拿了一件长大衣跟随他直奔追悼会现场。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从当时的新闻图片中，我们可以清楚地看见<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，参加陈毅追悼会的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">毛泽东大衣里面，露出的是睡衣。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪事件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">标志着文化大革命从理论到实践的彻底破产<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 毛泽东受到极大打击。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 国民经济经过几年<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">文化大革命<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的折腾消耗，极需恢复<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。毛泽东意识到，江青、张春桥、姚文元、王洪文等人，当打手可以，指望他们来抓工农业生产建设，将国民经济搞上去，是万万不可能的。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他们只会成事不足，败事有余。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 所以，毛泽东此时此刻，想<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">让一大批经验丰富的老干部<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出来收拾残局，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">虽然很<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无奈<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，却是明智<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">之<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">思。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 要想重新收买<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这些老帅、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老干部的人心，毛泽东参加陈毅追悼会<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是最合适的举动。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-11 19:09","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-11 19:09:57","ShortDate":"07-11 19:09","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":369,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_371_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第370楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" size=\"4\">当然，我们不排除这是林彪有意迷惑毛泽东，而故作的溢美之词，是一种策略...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<font size=\"5\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在似乎多这么说了.<\/font>&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-11 23:18","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-11 23:18:44","ShortDate":"07-11 23:18","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":370,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_372_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七二年二月，美国总统尼克松应邀来中国访问。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中美双方在上海联合发表的公<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">报<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">结束了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">两国二十多年<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">对抗，关系开始正常。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 四月二十四日，《人民日报》发表社论<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">《<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">惩前毖后，治病救人》。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 社论说，毛主席反复强调指出：“要相信百分之九十以上的干部是好的和比较好的。犯了错误的人，大多数是可以改的”，“打击面要小，教育面要宽”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 林彪事件后，毛泽东想重新利用老干部收拾局面的策略，开始付诸实践。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七二年五月，一场突如其来的龙卷风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">袭击了大圹圩<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大圹圩的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">安徽生产建设兵团二师九团的王台孜二连、三连和墩圩五连，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">受到重创。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">三连受灾最重。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这场龙卷风事先没有任何征兆，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">突如其来，从天而降<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当天，我带领各班、排下地分工栽秧，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">天气无任何异样。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">分好工刚回队部，就刮起大风。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高邮湖边刮大风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">常见，因此事先大家都<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在意。不料大风越刮越大，别说栽秧，人在秧地里站立都站立不住。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 于是大家开始踉踉仓仓撤回。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但回家的人很快又跑出来，卷缩在树下，因为房屋可怕地摇晃起来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我当时也刚从大田回来，刚到家就听到我屋后稻场上保管员秦正华在后面大声呼喊：“来人抢场啊，快来人啊<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">――<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 抢场，就是抢收稻场上的粮食。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我家房屋也在剧烈晃动，我知道门框一旦被挤<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">变形<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">想出都出不去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当时，我已经将大孩子“小土匪”送到金寨，交给了我母亲带。身边只带着女儿老二。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我叫小杨抱着一岁<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">多<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的女儿<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">离开房屋<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，让她抱着孩子坐在门前小树下<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">地面上躲风。我叮嘱她坐不住就和孩子趴在地下，不能站起来。接<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">着<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不放心，怕小杨顾不住孩子，女儿会被大风刮走。我又进屋找到一根绳子，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">将<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">女儿<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">用绳索捆绑在门前的树上。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 然后我向屋后稻场跑去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 稻场上，一个大粮囤捆绑好的大油布，被龙卷风掀开一角，囤圈里的粮食像轻灰一样被狂风吹走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保管员秦振华在粮囤边<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">冒着狂风暴雨，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">带<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">着十几个男女知青，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">围在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">粮囤边<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">紧紧<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">用手<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抓着油布不放<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那个被批斗的姓刘的老知青也在其中。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 油布一旦被大风卷走，不消说，这一大<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">囤<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">粮食顷刻间就会灰飞烟灭。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我冲上去，和他们一起抓紧油布。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 开始我还希图将油布用绳索<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">绑住固<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">定<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">起来<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，后来感觉油布抖动的力量太大，想用绳索<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">绑住<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">固定它根本不可能做到。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">身边一个上海女知青的上衣，被狂<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">掀起来套在她的头上。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">她<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的上身完全裸露，她<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">眼睛被衣服套住<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，什么也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看不见，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">她<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">又不敢将紧抓油布的手松开。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我只好松开<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">紧抓<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">油布的手，为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">身边的上海女知青<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">整好衣服。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 她感激地向我直点头。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 油布在龙卷风的狂吹下，在猛烈地抖动<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">欲挣脱<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们的手<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，随风而去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 尽管我们十几个人将油布紧紧拽着，依然敌不过狂风的肆虐。一阵狂风吹来，油布成降落伞状，将我们十几个人带起一尺多高。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我大喊一声：“危险！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">松手<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，一齐松手<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">！”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 众人手一松，油布即刻被吹起来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三丈见方的厚油布，像被单一样飘飘荡荡被狂风卷走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 姓刘的老知青怕自己会被安上破坏<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抓革命，促生产”的罪名，不敢先松手，他最后一个松手，差点被油布带走<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">卷上半空。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一大囤粮食，顷刻间化为乌有。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我连忙叫人散开，各自寻找安全的地方躲避<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">龙卷风<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-12 10:35","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-12 10:35:05","ShortDate":"07-12 10:35","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":371,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-12 18:59:48","delUser":"陈年老卤","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":255,"isHide":255,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-12 18:45","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-12 18:45:55","ShortDate":"07-12 18:45","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u31500300.htm","UserID":31500300,"UserName":"亦也真","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":372,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_374_0\"><p><font size=\"5\">这才是龙卷风。<\/font><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-12 18:59","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-12 18:59:37","ShortDate":"07-12 18:59","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":373,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_375_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十六，风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">灾<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">、救护周副团长和埋头学艺<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一大囤粮食顷刻间化为乌有不要紧，但风势并未减弱，眼见很多房屋上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">已经<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">压得结成板块的草顶，被龙卷风卷走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我祈祷，不要有人员伤亡。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 地面飞沙走石，我让大伙赶紧回去，刚刚将人员疏散开，在我们三连蹲点的副团长<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">周蜀生<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">身穿便衣，卷着裤腿<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">冒着狂风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">暴雨<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来到稻场。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周副团长在我们三连驻点，他是现役军人，四十多岁，矮矮胖胖的很结实，也很精干。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 狂风下，他跌跌撞撞来到稻场视察灾情。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他看见我们企图抢救粮囤未成，看见我在疏散人员。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他站在篮球架下四下观察。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我也在观察，我的目光透过周副团长的身影，在观察我家的屋子有无危险。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙卷风从东向西而来，我家的屋子在最西头一间，显然没有危险，但房顶<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上的茅草，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">被掀走一半。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 令我惊讶的是，眼前一个石磙被大风吹动，从稻场上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">由东<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">向西滚过去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 俗话<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">所说<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的“大风吹不走石磙”的真理，此刻成为谎言。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我立即意识到，这个石磙，是压在钢管篮球架支架下面废弃的石磙。这个石磙是我们喜欢打篮球的人为固定篮球架，自己压上去的。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我抬眼一看，篮球架的底座失去石磙重量压力的固定，正在剧烈摇晃，已经摇摇欲坠。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 而周副团长还正在篮球架下观察，在思考着什么。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他丝毫没有觉察到危险即将发生。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 间不容发，我急速冲到周副团长身边，抓住他的左臂，用力一拽。周副团长猝不及防，被迫转身，踉踉仓仓前倾两步，险些栽倒。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我也随着惯性<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">冲<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出险地。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 钢管篮球架几乎同时被狂风吹倒，篮板沉重地砸在地面<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，篮板即刻折断。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 倒下的篮球架，距离我俩仅有二尺。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这才叫千钧一发，看得我一阵后怕。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周副团长愣愣看着我，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">回过神来，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">嘴唇吓得在颤抖。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 狂风大作，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">暴雨倾盆。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">什么<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来不及说，我将周副团长拉回到他的临时住处。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 接着，就听到外面有人高喊：“不好啦！裔师傅家的房子倒啦！卢排长和他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">家<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的小三子都被压在屋子里面啊！”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 卢排长就是裔师傅的夫人卢<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">新<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">民，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们六安知青都喊她老大，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">她是女生知青排排长。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 没说的，先去救人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他家住在我家前一栋，东头第一间。龙卷风从东而来，房屋山墙的泥浆中没有水泥<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、石灰<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，都是泥巴<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在龙卷风<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和大雨<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的横扫下，倒塌实属难免。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙卷风的灾害，不是大面积的，是一条百余米之内的长线。凡是龙卷风中心地带经过的地点，灾情会很重。王台孜二连会计王建淮的母亲，也是死于这次风灾。他家的房屋被龙卷风刮倒，老人遇难。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 数天后，王台孜的稻田里发现一只渔船，这条渔船显然是被大风从高邮湖里卷出，并飞越大堤来到<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了我们的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">稻田<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这都<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是这次龙卷风的杰作。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 裔师傅和卢新民家的房子被龙卷风刮倒，裔师傅开拖拉机下田了，不在家。卢新民与他家的小三子被压在里面，我们不知道卢新民母子的死活，焦虑万分。&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们自动组成二十多有经验的老知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和老工<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人开始清理、清除她家倒塌房子的砖块、倒塌<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">下来<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的房梁和茅草。救援<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人员多了也用不上，反而<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">碍事。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 所幸在抢救中，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们听到了卢新民在废墟里的呼叫，并能和我们对话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当我们得知卢新民母子在龙卷风来时，他家大门变形，人出不来，她母子都躲在床底下，只受到轻微擦伤时，人们方长吁一口气。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_375_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"15-07-12 20:37","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-12 20:40:10","ShortDate":"07-12 20:40","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":374,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_376_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 下地干活的人，有的人不在龙卷风中心地带，只知道刮大风，没什么感觉。只有在龙卷风中心走过的地带，人们才能感受到龙卷风的威力和可怕。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周颂平告诉我，龙卷风来时，他还在耙地。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 风越来越大，耕田班实在无法耙地了，他们就卸下耙，牵牛往回走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 走着走着就无法行走了，人被大风刮的顺风乱跑，他们只好以田埂作掩体，躺在背风一面的田埂下躲风。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 开始，耕田耙地的老水牛还能站着，歪着用头用一只牛角顶风，似乎在讥笑人类的软弱。后来水牛也渐渐不支，调头改用屁股<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">对着<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">风。再后来牛屁股也受不了龙卷风的暴虐，索性也卧倒在田埂下躲起来了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长和罗指导员当天都下地了，他俩的境遇，应该和耕田班的人差不多。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙卷风说来就来，说走就走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但龙卷风在极短的时间里，给我们三连带来极大的灾害。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 家家房上的稻草房顶，几乎都被龙卷风刮走，连大田里刚栽种的秧苗都被刮走。电话线被刮断，许多树木被刮倒。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 救灾和灾后重建工作，十分繁重。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连队为此召开动员大会，号召全连干部战士，重建家园，努力生产，将龙卷风灾害带来的损失补回来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 指导员特地请驻点的周副团长讲话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周副团长没说别的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大道理<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，只是将我那天在台风中带人抢场，和救他的事情在会上述说了一遍。对我的“临危不惧，奋不顾身，英勇救人”的行为，大加赞赏，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十分感激，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当众向我表示感谢。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我当时心想，我能不救你吗？你要是被篮球架砸死了，我\r\n在你身边安然无恙，怎么向大家解释？没准，还有人会说是我将你推到篮球架下面，是故意谋杀呢！<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在阶级斗争的理论指导下，什么阴毒的革命<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">联想都有可能<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出现，都不足<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">奇。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 因为赵连长和罗指导员不知道这<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">件<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">事，二<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">听后<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都很惊奇。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-13 16:48","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-13 16:48:00","ShortDate":"07-13 16:48","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":375,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_377_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第376楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" size=\"4\">在阶级斗争的理论指导下，什么阴毒的革命联想都有可能出现，都不足为奇。...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<br />\r\n<font size=\"5\">别说这种有可能性的推测了,就是那些毫无可能性的推测都会产生,以证明阶级斗争观念强.<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-13 19:33","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-13 19:33:04","ShortDate":"07-13 19:33","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":376,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_378_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这年夏天，我开始学习<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">画<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">油画。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我学油画，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">除了我自幼爱好绘画外，还有一个不可告人的目的，那就是想以后调离兵团<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，能<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">成为一个文化艺术工作者。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">除了绘画，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">喜爱美术、音乐、文学，尤其是喜爱戏剧、电影文学。在诗词曲赋里，我特别喜欢元曲。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 昆曲剧本《西厢记》、《桃花扇》里面的清词丽句，让我爱不释手。这个时期，我看<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很多古今中外戏剧理论的书籍、剧本和各种杂类书籍。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当时，我得到一小本手抄的赵朴初先生的散曲，让我大开眼界，现摘录两首，聊以怀旧。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 之一：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 听话听反话，不会是傻瓜。可爱唤做“可憎”，亲人唤做“冤家”。夜里演戏叫做“旦<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，叫做“净”的恰是满脸大黑花。高贵的王侯，偏要称“孤”道“寡”，你说他是谦虚还是自夸？君不见，“小小小小的老百姓”，却是个大大大大的野心家<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">哈哈！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 之二：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 听话听反话，一点也不差。“高举红旗”，却早是黑幡高挂。“共产主义”，原来是子孙万世家天下。大呼“共诛共讨”的顶呱呱，谁知道，首逆元凶就是他！到头来、落得个仓皇逃命，落得折戟沉沙。这件事儿可不假，这光头跟着那光头去也！这才是，代价最小、最小，收获最大、最大！是吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在看来，虽然赵先生的政治观点有待商榷，但在艺术上的确技法娴熟，将古典散曲艺术形式<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">运用<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的得心应手，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">炉火纯青。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我如饥似渴，饥不择食地看书，往往<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看书<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">能通宵达旦。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当时，我创作的油画肖像作品《兵团女战士》，参加了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">安徽<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">省建设兵团美展。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 同时，我创作的中篇小说《青竹岭》<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">初<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">稿，安徽文艺编辑部很感兴趣。后因安徽文艺编辑部再三要求，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">该作品<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">必须按“三突出”创作原则来写，我无法接受，书稿被我放弃。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在画油画的时候，我的创作力较差，但临摹的功夫尚可。我临摹汤小铭先生的油画《永不休战》鲁迅肖像，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">几<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">能乱真，让人称奇。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">按印刷品临摹绘制的大型油画《毛主席去安源》，也颇受好品。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这年，我有幸和著名画家张悲鹭先生有了书信往来。也可以说，我们是未谋面的忘年莫逆之交。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 张悲鹭先生民国六年生于四川省乐山市，先后在成都东方美专、杭州西湖艺院及日本国上野美专深造。解放前曾创办并任西南艺术学院（设重庆）<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">院长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、凌云艺术学院（设重庆北培）<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">院长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、凌云美术学院（设上海）<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">院长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，当过上海美术研究所所长。一九四九年后，张悲鹭先生继任该所所长。一九五七年奉中央教育部派遣支援安徽，在安徽师范学院（现为安徽师范大学）任教，后回上海“诗画廊”从事组织和编辑工作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“文革”后<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">张悲鹭先生任安徽省文史馆馆员。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 张悲鹭精通水墨、水粉、油画，山水、花鸟、飞禽、走兽、人物，尤以画虎为长，为全国四大画虎名家之一。其画风是将中国画、日本画和西洋画之特点<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">综合融会，自成一派。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一九四一年四月，张悲鹭在重庆<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">作巨幅<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">长卷《百虎图》<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">高二尺、横长十八丈。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">郭沫若<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">见此巨构<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">诗情澎湃，当即挥毫<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，在画上写下<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">壮丽沉郁的七言古体长诗八十八行。继后有田汉、茅盾、史良、沈钧儒、叶圣陶、梅兰芳、冯玉祥、于右任等一百多位全国知名人士<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在该图上题诗。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">张悲鹭后<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">因从事革命宣传工作，被国民党下令通缉，一九四零年被上海警备司令部逮捕。后由宋庆龄、于右任、史良、梅兰芳等出面营救出狱。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">张悲鹭先生在皖南大学（今安徽师范大学）任教期间，与我二姐夫肖汉友有师生之谊。先生在“文革”中饱受迫害，被下放在合肥郊区撮镇农场干<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">农<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">活。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有一次张悲鹭先生去金寨出差，我二姐夫、二姐热情接待了他，并要求他指点我画画。张悲鹭先生一口答应，苦于我们各在东西，俱都身陷困境，难以见面，只能鸿雁往来。我们在书信中谈人生，谈艺术，谈遭遇，谈家常，是名符其实的忘年交<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 张悲鹭先生在信中告诉我，他原名<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">清<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">泉，因与心仪之人罗清鹭相恋。但罗清鹭被父逼迫，要将她嫁与豪绅而愤然投江自尽。张<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">清泉<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为哀念女友，改名悲鹭。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 世人有关于张悲鹭先生为纪念恋人改名的传闻，但传闻毕竟是传闻，先生给我的亲笔信，则是此说的第一手佐证资料。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 张悲鹭先生于一九九三年病逝。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 张悲鹭先生为实实在在帮助我学习绘画，给他的学生、天长县文化馆的画家葛彬尧写了一封信，要他全力以赴帮我解决在学习绘画上的困难。我曾多次到天长<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">县文化馆<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">求教于葛彬尧先生<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">葛先生送过我很多绘画的学习材料和美术理论书籍，还送我很多很昂贵的油画颜料，对我的帮助十分巨大。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 油画颜料很贵，我不能全指望葛彬尧先生赠送，有时只好自掏腰包购买，使我的经济压力很大。在临摹《毛主席去安源》这幅油画时，我是将家里的一床被单，当做油画布蒙在画框上画的。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">此，小杨与我大闹一<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">场<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我苦<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">学<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">二胡、乱写词曲，信马由缰、好奇地在艺术的芳草地上寻觅、探索。这时期，我特别想离开兵团，能成为一名文化艺术工作者。<br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_378_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"15-07-13 21:38","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-13 23:46:31","ShortDate":"07-13 23:46","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":377,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_379_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第378楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" size=\"4\">我特别想离开兵团，能成为一名文化艺术工作者。...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<font size=\"5\">&nbsp;有志者,事竟成.<\/font><br /><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 12:37","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 12:37:15","ShortDate":"07-14 12:37","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":378,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_380_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我开始写信给我姐姐，请她设法帮我调动工作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我母亲、弟弟和二姐一家都在金寨，回老家六安已无意义，只能去金寨。但我只在金寨念过两年小学，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有任何人脉关系，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">因此只能依靠二姐和二姐夫帮我奔走求人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25.2pt;margin:0pt;padding-bottom:0pt;padding-left:0pt;padding-right:0pt;padding-top:0pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">国营单位的工人，调动工作十分艰难。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25.2pt;margin:0pt;padding-bottom:0pt;padding-left:0pt;padding-right:0pt;padding-top:0pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">“农林四场”的工人要求调动工作，不仅困难，还只能对口调动，根本没有选择工作的自由。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25.2pt;margin:0pt;padding-bottom:0pt;padding-left:0pt;padding-right:0pt;padding-top:0pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><span style=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">建设兵团名义上是解放军部队编制，很好听。但在兵团战士调动工作时，却是按对口“农林四场”的政策办理。杂牌军本质，一览无余。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25.2pt;margin:0pt;padding-bottom:0pt;padding-left:0pt;padding-right:0pt;padding-top:0pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n“农林四场”即国营农、林、牧、渔四行业单位，简称“农林四场”。<\/span><span style=\"color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;text-transform:none;\">这些单位的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">工人调动工作十分<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">困难。不仅困难，还<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">只能对口调动，根本没有选择工作的自由。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 建设兵团名义上是解放军部队编制，很好听。但在兵团战士调动工作时，却是按对口“农林四场”的政策办理。杂牌军本质，一览无余。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “农林四场”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的工人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">调动工作时<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">首先是要当地劳动局给你出具接收证明，即商调函，有了商调函，你所在单位才会给你开调令。而<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">劳动局<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出具接收证明的条件，是得有单位愿意接收你。各单位的经费<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都是上级的固定拨款，增加人员就是增加<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">本单位<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">开支，故而各单位谁也不想增加人员。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二姐和二姐夫为我调动工作<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，多方多次送礼<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">求人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">屈尊<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无奈<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">冷遇<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">尴尬，言之不尽。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对于调动工作，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我只能抱着<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">尽人力，听天命<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的宗旨，耐心等待时机。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 15:49","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 15:49:28","ShortDate":"07-14 15:49","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":379,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_381_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十七，高邮湖防汛和放电影风波<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙卷风刚过，就是夏汛，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要到高邮湖堤坝上防汛<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抢险<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高邮湖<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">上<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">并非只有长堤绿柳，湖帆点点，碧水烟波和海市蜃楼的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">迷人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">美景。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高邮湖的龙卷风可怕，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">它<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的湖水<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">发起威来，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">煞是吓人。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">每当汛期，湖水高涨，风助水势，浪花汹涌。惊雷暴雨，狂涛拍岸。站在大堤之上，有地动天摇之撼，让人不寒而栗。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们大圹圩农场的防水大堤，十分高大坚固，一般不会出现险情。但周围农村的圩区，堤坝不是很理想，都很矮小。汛期一到，高邮湖湖水暴涨，险象环生。破圩的事情，时有发生。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我亲见一圩破堤，圩内<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">几个<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">农妇仍然在安心割稻、抢收庄稼。对家园即将被淹没的险情，视而不见，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">她们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">显然已经习惯破堤。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次防汛<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抢险<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我们三连的任务，是帮助湖滨公社挑土方，加固一段可能会出现险情的堤坝。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这也算是我们九团和地方政府的拥军爱民活动，军民携手<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">合作抗洪。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 连队抽调一百多名男、女战士，组成突击队。大家自带工具和日常生活用品，奔赴湖滨公社的险情堤坝。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长留守连部，罗指导员带队，我负责<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">防汛的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">后勤和监工<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 突击队所有人吃<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">喝<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都在工地，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">夜晚借农家的房子铺地铺睡觉。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">日以继夜，苦战在防汛第一线。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这种抢险性的加固堤坝，就是将原先低矮、薄弱的堤坝增高增厚，需要大量土方。而这些土方，或挑或抬，都是人工运输，十分累人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 女突击队员都是城市知青，为照顾她们，安排男突击队员运土。或挑、或抬，自由组合。女突击队员挖土上筐，挖土上筐虽然比抬土、挑土轻松，但也很吃力。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们在大堤上奋战了一个多星期，终于胜利在望，可以提前一天完成任务。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最后一天下午，赵连长来到我们抗洪工地，他告诉我们一个好消息。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长说，为奖励我们这次顺利完成任务，他特地到团部，请宣传股安排电影队晚上到我们三连，放映一场新艺术片《钢琴伴唱红灯记》。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 并说团宣传股已经同意。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长要求我们再接再厉，争取再提前两小时收工，好拔营回连队看电影。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当时，连队的文艺活动极少，看电影是唯一的文艺享受。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团部开始许诺的每月看一次电影，无法兑现，有时两个月我们都看不上一场电影。且电影除了宣传毛主席革命路线的《新闻纪录片》，就是“三战”和“八戏”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “三战”为《地道战》、《地雷战》、《南征北战》，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n“八戏”就是八个样板戏。偶然也有什么《列宁在十月》、《鲜花盛开的村庄》之类，都是看过不知道多少次的玩意了。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">虽然这些东西大家都看厌了，但《钢琴伴唱红灯记》我们是只在广播里听过，没看过。在那种文化荒漠的时间段，像《钢琴伴唱红灯记》这种换汤不换药的东西，也能使人有新鲜感。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长的这个好消息，激励了大家的干劲。离家多日，大家也都想回家了。即使是没有家庭的单身男、女突击队员，在连部也都有一张栖身的床铺，和在工地滚铺的临时凑乎生活，毕竟不同。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 因此，大伙一鼓作气，在四点钟提前按质按量完成了任务。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长要我提前回连部，派驴车去团部接放员和放映设备，安排人员帮助放映员架设银幕、喇叭，安放发电机。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我回到连队，将一切按部就班准备就绪。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 15:53","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 15:53:25","ShortDate":"07-14 15:53","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":380,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_382_0\"><img src=\"http://imgs.xici.net/_img/emot/panda/3.gif\" /><font size=\"5\">翘首企足<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u20916672/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_382_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"15-07-14 16:15","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 16:16:35","ShortDate":"07-14 16:16","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d214637218.u20916672.htm","UserID":20916672,"UserName":"周家小五","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":381,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_383_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第382楼 @周家小五 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">翘首企足 ...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<br />\r\n<font size=\"5\">谢谢关注！<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 16:50","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 16:50:24","ShortDate":"07-14 16:50","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":382,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_384_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大家吃完晚饭，三三两两手拿小<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竹<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">椅、条凳，来到队部前的空地银幕前，静候看电影。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 天色渐暗，放映员高云亦将准备工作做好了，就在他正要放映时，他接到团部宣传股电话，要他先带机器、器材和影片回团部先放，然后再到三连来放。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 原来这天安徽生产建设兵团二师师部组织的“学大寨交流会”来到了我们团，与会人员吃完饭，团政治部祁主任请师长和各团负责人来到办公大楼上，要请他们看这部电影。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们连在放电影现场的人，听到这个消息都很气愤。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 劳累一天，宣传股安排好在我们连晚上放电影，这么多人的事情，凭什么说变卦就变卦？领导干部们难道就高贵一些，非得先看？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 群众不服，不准放映员高云走，要他放完电影再走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云找到我，要我去说服大家让他先回团部放，团部放完后再来三连放。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我对高云说，一个多小时不就放完了吗？为什么不能放完影片再回团部放？这样来回折腾有意思吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但高云不敢<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">先<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在我们连放，坚持要服从命令，要先回团部放。而三连的人不答应，不准他拆卸放映机。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 两下僵持起来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我知道这个情况后，立刻预感到这件事情不好收拾<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三连的老职工、老知青和新知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不会让放映员高云走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"> 官民矛盾，由来已久，借此发酵，事成必然。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">而三连的领导，谁决定先给团部放，谁就会在三连威信尽失，遭人唾弃。可谁抗拒团部的命令，谁也不会有好果子吃。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为赵连长着想，我找到他，劝他躲起<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我对赵连长说，别问发生什么事情，你人不在，罪名就安不到你头上。而且，群众在激愤之下，未必会听从命令。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">对团首长这样的做法<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也生气，也无奈，就远远躲起来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指员家在团部，他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">从防汛工地直接回家<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的，不知道这件事<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 放映员高云<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">见我不帮他说话，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">只好找赵连长<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来解围<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">但<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">已经<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">找不到赵连长<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也知道找其他几个副职解决不了问题。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他和我熟悉，于是他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">又<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">找到我，和我商量怎么办。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我说：你要是按时放映，现在不就快放完了吗？现在这种局面，已经引起众怒，我这个小文书说话能管用吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我要高云别犹豫，抓紧放映，然后我派驴车送你回去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但高云不敢违背祁主任命令，他没办法，只身摸黑跑回团部交差去了。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 师长和各团的团长、政委<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，都在团部办公大楼的楼顶上等着看电影。两个小时过去了，也没看成，也不知道是怎么回事。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 于是他们就拿我们团的团长、政委开涮，嘲笑他俩<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无能<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团长、政委没办法，也不知什么<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">情<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">况。他俩一面派人弄西瓜来堵客人的嘴，一面将政治部祁主任狠狠训<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一顿，严命他立即设法将放映员和电影找来放。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云回到团部，找到<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">宣传<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">股长，将三连不准拉放映机的情况向宣传股<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一一作了汇报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 宣传股长也傻了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 事情是他自己安排的，现在出现这种情况，他当不了家，带着高云，将事情如实汇报给团政治部祁主任。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 祁主任一挥手，对宣传股长下令：立即派团部吉普车叫高云去三连拉机器，就说这是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">政治部的命令，是政治任务，谁也不能阻拦。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云乘坐着吉普车又回到三连来了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 放映机四周围满了人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云盛气凌人地在众人面前，将祁主任的命令传达一遍。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一个老知青大喊一声：“我们要学习革命样板戏，谁反对我们学习革命样板戏，谁就是林秃子林彪！”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一个上海知青故意挑衅地责问放映员高云说：“祁主任是不是就是说我们发烧不到三十九度，就得下地干活的那个家伙？”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云傻了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不知道哪位老兄又喊了一声：<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谁反对我们学习革命样板戏，谁就是反对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们敬爱的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">江青同志，我们就要将他打倒！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">砸烂他的狗头！”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大伙乐的乐，骂的骂。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 高云见机不妙，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">只好<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">乘坐吉普车又<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">重新<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">转回团部。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">时已凌晨一点有余。<br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 16:53","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 16:53:52","ShortDate":"07-14 16:53","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":383,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_385_0\"><div style=\"background:#eef6ff;border-bottom:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-left:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-right:#77aaee 1px dotted;border-top:#77aaee 1px dotted;margin:6px;padding-bottom:6px;padding-left:6px;padding-right:6px;padding-top:6px;\"><b><font\r\ncolor=\"#3366ee\">以下是引用 第384楼 @半醉汉 的话：<\/font><\/b><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\" size=\"4\">谁反对我们学习革命样板戏，谁就是反对我们敬爱的江青同志，我们就要将他打倒！砸烂他的狗头！”...<\/font><\/div>\r\n<br />\r\n<font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 当年，这也是吵架斗殴的理由.<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 17:18","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 17:18:57","ShortDate":"07-14 17:18","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":384,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_386_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十八，调查“抢”电影事件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;四五十多分钟后，吉普车又转回来了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员冷着脸走下车，高云也跟着走下来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 显然，团首长们知道再派其他人来三连只会激化矛盾，他们只好半夜三更<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来到<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">三连的罗指导员<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">家，将他<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">喊了起来<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，要他来解决这个难题<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 你们连出的事情，就命令你这个当指导员的去解决。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员对大家说，别的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都不说了，现在师首长和其他团的首长，都在团部等着看电影。他们是客人，我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是主人，我们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大家发扬风格，先让客人看，然后我们再看。耽误了大家的休息时间，我当家，全连明天上午放<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">假<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">半天。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员请大家顾全大局。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 县官不如现管，连队的直接领导出面调解，不看佛面看僧面，大家不好再当面顶撞，但依然七嘴八舌表露出不满情绪。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">最后，罗指导员担保影片在团部放完后，立即赶回三连连夜放映<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。在这种<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">情况下，大家才没有意见，同意放映员高云将放映设备拉走。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 已近凌晨两点了，谁也没有离开放映场地。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谁都能看出，大家这时候已经不是要看电影，是在赌气。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">凌晨四点，吉普车<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">又<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">将放映员高云和机器送回<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">三连<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，三连等<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">着<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看电影的人，除了妇女孩子，大部分人并未散去。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电影结束时已近早晨六点，红日早已高升。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这件事，团党委不知自<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我反<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">省，反认为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是三连<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有阶级敌人在背后操纵，蒙蔽群众和团党委作对，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">破坏<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">师部组织的“学大寨交流会”，是阶级斗争新动向。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 政治部祁主任派人来到三连驻点调查，查了几天，一无所获。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赵连长和罗指导员以及整个党支部，都认为团党委此举，是小题大做。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但调查人员秉承上级旨意，认为这是破坏我们团接待师部组织的“学大寨交流会”，是阶级敌人有意制造的政治事件。而三连人员结构复杂，暗藏的阶级敌人非常狡猾，落后分子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们又<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">盘根错节<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">针插不进，水泼不透。连队党支部<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">缺乏阶级斗争的敏锐性，调查工作难以开展。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在他们心里，这个事件一定是暗藏的阶级敌人在背后操纵、蛊惑造成的。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 盖因大圹圩农场组建成兵团后，军人初来，他们在制止派性斗争，纠正无政府主义时，起到了一定作用。但在生产建设、行政管理上，明显缺乏经验。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">省兵团<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在组织路线上，从连队到团部，司令部、政治部、后勤部各机关部门，党、政一把手都是军人担任。地方干部工作能力再强，资格再老，都是副职。这样一来，军人和地方干部的矛盾，日益加深。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 军人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">管理地方生产建设的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">经验<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不足，工作方法简单、主观的弱点，逐渐暴露。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对这些，军人不从正常的反思、反省来总结经验，而是以阶级斗争为纲，希图在对方阵营中找出阶级敌人，打击对方。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次团部宣传股调度安排在三连放电影，在放映机已经安装好，即将开映的情况下，团部为媚上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要先<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在团部<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">放电影。并强行下令将电影撤走，引起三连群众不满，扣留了放映机。这件事<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在全团<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">造成了不好影响，给全师的“学大寨交流会”留下阴影。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在这件事情上，军人们丝毫没有想到是自己安排不周，本身毫无组织纪律、随心所欲造成的，反而要嫁祸于人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 其实，他们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当时<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">只要向师首长和客人说明一下情况，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">电影<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">迟点放没有<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">什么<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">关系。何况、师首长和其它团的客人们，早就看过这个电影，甚至<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还有<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不喜欢看这种电影<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但军人们瞒上压下，仗势欺人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">已成习惯<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他们在主观上<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">臆造敌人，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">希望<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">天上能掉下一个阶级敌人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。没有阶级敌人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就要制造阶级敌人。只有这样，他们才<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">好挥舞阶级斗争的大棍，打垮<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">想要打倒、打垮的人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在他们心里，这个阶级敌人的人选，最好就是我。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 若能将我打成阶级敌人，对老职工、老知青、新知青，甚至老干部，都能起到震慑作用。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但事与愿违，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团政治部在三连的多次调查，均一无所得。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团党委一厢情愿，请求师部派<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">专案组来三连调查。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二师师部偏听偏信，或许他们也有难言之隐，居然派了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">由<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">四个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">师直机关<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">员<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">组成<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">调查组进驻三连，专门调查此事。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有趣的是，师部没有和团部联合调查，而是独立调查。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这表明，师部对团部的一面之词，并不完全相信。同时，师部<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">派<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">调查人员，也没有用“<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抢电影<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">专案组”的名义，而是用“调查组”的名义来到三连，没有按团党委的设想办。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这也使团党委很尴尬、很无趣。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据说，周副团长在师长面前<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">抱怨<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说，三连到底发生了什么案件？要派“专案组”下来查？我在三连驻点，我怎么不知道发生过什么案件？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不就是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大家都<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">争着<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要先<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">场电影吗？<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当天晚上在三连放电影，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这是团宣传股自己安排的，能怪人家基层连队的人吗？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">听说有人怀疑甄远东是阶级敌人，这不是笑话吗？这个人我了解，他是个见义勇为的好青年。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我想，新来乍到的师部“调查组”人员，也一定知道我曾经是“保岳派”的头头，他们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会向老党委书记、现在的副<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">岳中林了解我的情况。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我并不指望别人为我说什么好话，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">但<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">相信<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大家都<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">实事求是地说话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 所以我一点也不在乎。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “调查组”在三连调查多日，每天深入群众了解情况，大致摸清了“抢电影”事件的来龙去脉。也了解了我以前的一些事情，他们认为我没有什么出格的言行，决定收兵。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一个“调查组”成员<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在离开前<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">跟我开玩笑说，哈哈，有人说你<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">甄远东<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是一个坚定的无产阶级革命战士<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">呢<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我笑道，他们可能不知道“无产阶级革命战士”比“无产阶级革命家”的规格还要高。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这个“调查组”成员说，知道知道，他们知道。他们这样说的目的，就是向我们摊牌，别想查出你有什么问题。哈哈，\r\n你在三连混得不错啊！<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我说，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谈不上混得不错，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一般化<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">而已。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">反正我的处事原则是硬的不怕，软的不欺。好事做不了，坏事绝不做。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 临行，这个“调查组”成员对我说<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">：“<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有人在我们面前说，我们三连有两个党支部。一个是共产党的党支部，还有一个是地下党的党支部。这个地下党党支部的头子，就是你。我们调查组要他拿出证据，他说他没有证据，只有感觉。甄远东同志，你给人有这样的感觉，很危险啊！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">”<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我说，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不做亏心事，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">半夜<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">鬼来心不惊。别人怎么想我不管，我不会按别人的想法去生活。顺大流、拍马屁最安全，我不是不会，是不愿意那样做。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 至此，“抢电影”事件告一段落，最后不了了之。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但我在团党委一些人的眼里<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">成了危险人物。尤其是政治部祁主任，在他心里，我就应<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">该<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是一个阶级敌人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他遗憾的是，下了这么大的功夫，没抓住我任何把柄。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团党委下这么大的功夫整我，我也生气。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 搞阶级斗争不是你一家的专利，我也会。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我等待机会，也打算在适当的时候<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">玩一玩阶级斗争这个把戏<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，对<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这些<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">想整我的人<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">还以颜色<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-14 22:07","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-14 22:07:20","ShortDate":"07-14 22:07","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":385,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_387_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">六十九，“十大”和“批林批孔”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七二年，人们在惊讶、猜疑、反思和顺大流的状态中过去了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七三年春，中共中央作出《关于恢复邓小平同志党的组织生活和国务院副总理职务的决定》。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们对此，喜欢引用的一句著名的电影台词开玩笑，叫“我胡汉三又回来了”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七一年林彪死后，到一九七二年八月，邓小平两次写信向毛泽东<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">检讨<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，表示<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">要<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">效忠毛泽东，愿意为党，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">国家、<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">人民做些工作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不甘冷落之心，跃然纸上。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 毛泽东<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">受林彪事件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">刺激<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和打击<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">下<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，正要收买人心，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">见到邓小平的信后，他当即<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">下达指示，肯定了邓小平的长处和功绩。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 别管你职位多高，有无罪证，是敌是友，都在他老人家一念之间。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七三年春，邓小平从江西回到北京后，于四月十二日参加了欢迎柬埔寨西哈努克亲王到北京的宴会，闪亮登场<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，分外引人注目<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五月，中共中央开会讨论了批林整风问题。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 八月二十四日至二十八日，中国共产党第十次全国代表大会在北京举行。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会议一致通过毛泽东主持起草的政治报告，王洪文作了关于修改党章的报告和新的《中国共产党章程》。一些在“文化大革命”中受到排斥和打击迫害的老同志，如邓小平、王稼祥、乌兰夫、李井泉、谭震林、廖承志等，被选为中央委员。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这标志着被毛泽东打倒的老革命们重新崛起。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 同时，也展现出毛泽东恩威并施的统治手段卓有成效。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大大小小的老干部们，在文革中被批判、被斗争被戴高帽、被拳打脚踢、被游街示众，受尽奇耻大辱<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">此刻<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">能够复出，可以东山再起，但<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竟无一人为自尊<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">而愿意<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">终老南山。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">官，他们宠辱不惊，真正做到了忍辱负重。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 究其因，他们是为米折腰。离开体制，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就失去了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">能<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">各取所需的共产主义饭碗。吃饭大似天，何况吃<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">特权<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">饭<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，特别的饭。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “十大”批判了林彪反革命集团的罪行，却确认“九大的政治路线和组织路线都是正确的”，让人感觉很可笑，很滑稽。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “九大”在党章上规定林彪是毛泽东的革命接班人，他们似乎忘记了，忘到九霄云外去了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在这次修改的党章“总纲”中，删去了关于林彪为接班人的规定。可是，耻辱是删不去的了。留在中国人心底的疑问与阴影，也挥之不去。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “十大”仍然提出要“坚持无产阶级专政下继续革命”的理论<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，这也是林彪在“九大”政治报告上强调的话<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可以说，这次会议根本没有纠正“九大”的错误，反而<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">越走越远，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">反而<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">使以江青为首的四人帮<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">反动<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">势力得到加强。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据说，大会闭幕式后，毛泽东年迈体弱，无法站立。为避免尴尬，周恩来只好请代表们先走，说毛主席要目送大家。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 真乃感人至深，玩人至深。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七三年底，根据毛泽东的意见，八大军区司令员对调。可见林彪虽死，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">余<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">威仍在，毛泽东对军队戒心重重。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这时候，批林整风最后发展成“批林批孔”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “林”是指林彪，“孔”是孔子。风马牛不相及的二人，被捆绑在一起批。目的是要斗垮斗臭林彪和孔子。对今古这两个文人武将，进行各种诬蔑。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七四年一月，毛泽东批发中共中央一号文件，转发了由江青主持选编的《林彪与孔孟之道》（材料之一），全国开始了“批林批孔”运动。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 毛泽东想借助“批林批孔”来统一全党的认识，多次提出“批孔丘”，“批尊孔反法”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 江青等人接过这个口号，指使迟群、谢静宜在清华和北大成立“大批判组”，编辑林彪与孔孟之道的材料。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最后，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">“批林批孔”发展成一个声势浩大的政治运动。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<t