d":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":389,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_391_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七四年四月，三连派我和老知青周颂平、李永光三人到团部，参加师部派人来宣讲的“批林批孔”培训班。培训班主要是学习中共中央《关于批林批孔运动几个问题的通知》和一些辅导资料。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “批林批孔”培训班要求我们这些人回去后，要联系实际，深入广泛地开展“批林批孔”运动。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中央《关于批林批孔运动几个问题的通知》上说：“要欢迎群众联系本地区阶级斗争和两条路线斗争实际所提出的批评。有极少数领导干部，不批林，不批孔，捂盖子，怕群众，甚至采取恶劣手段挑动群众斗群众，破坏革命，破坏生产，煽动经济主义，破坏知识青年上山下乡，这是完全错误的。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 上面的文字都是一些不<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">着<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">边际的话，按这种文字精神对照一下，团领导干部<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">谁都能拉出来批一批。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我和周颂平、李永光商量一下，决定借“批林批孔”这股阴冷的东风，将团政治部祁主任，当成是“林彪、孔老二”在我团的代理人，将他当活靶子打一打。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 让他也尝尝阶级斗争的滋味。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-16 19:38","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-16 19:38:19","ShortDate":"07-16 19:38","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":390,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_392_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">七十，炮打祁主任<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们之所以<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">瞄上<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">政治部祁主任，并不是仅仅因为他在放电影风波中想将我打成阶级敌人，我的气量还不至于这么狭窄。这里面，有好几个原因。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一是此人对下极其凶狠，声言兵团战士要“轻伤不下火线”，不是大病就必须下地干活。他命令医院和各连卫生室，对病号“发烧不到三十九度的，不许开病假条”。他在兵团战士<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的心中，人人痛恨。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二是此人在军人中亦口碑不佳，遭人嫉恨。团部许多老资格的军队干部，都说他是坐“直升飞机”升上来的，对他多是笑脸相迎，侧目而视。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三是此人一贯高高在上，目中无人。他从不下连队，更看不起地方干部。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">同事中没人缘，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">群众中没基础。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 四是此人阶级斗争观念极强，最喜欢对别人上纲上线，无论发生什么事，他都喜欢草木皆兵，都要往阶级斗争新动向上扯。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次我们借“批林批孔”运动，正好可以“以其人之道，反制其人之身”，还以颜色。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五是我们要向团党委提出要求，星期天和法定假，应该按国家规定执行放假。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大圹圩农场自成立那天起，就是每月只放一天假。这本身是违法的，工人为此抗争多年，奈何<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">权大于法，掌权的人对此一合理要求不予理睬<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">基层民众<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">手中无权<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无选票<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，只能任人摆布。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在这时候提出落实法定假，一定会深得人心。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我估计，将矛头对准祁主任个人，不是对着团政治部，团党委就不会为他个人被批判而为他说话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们也做好了准备，如果团党委要出头为祁主任说话，那我们就连团党委一起炮轰。届时，我们将认定团党委是我们团“林彪、孔老二”代理人的保护伞，让团党委引火烧身。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谁敢反对我们无产阶级“批林批孔”？谁敢反对我们保卫\r\n毛主席？谁敢反对我们保卫无产阶级文化大革命的旗手江青？<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们就铁了心要跟毛主席干革命了，谁怕谁啊？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 回到三连，我们在大会上传达了省兵团有关“批林批孔”的文件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会后<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">开始发动群众，准备材料，写好充足的炮打政治部祁主任大字报以备用。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那些新<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一听说我们要炮打政治部祁主任，一个个心里乐开花。他们摩拳擦掌，欢欣鼓舞。在学校，他们还小，没赶上能亲自上阵斗人，没想到下放到兵团了，还能遇到这样新鲜的事情。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员和赵连长也被连续不断的政治运动弄晕了，对我们的行动，有些无所适从<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，也有些担心<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。无所适从<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，是不知道上面到底要做什么。担心，是怕耽误生产。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我劝他俩别担心，我向他们保证，“批林批孔”批祁主任，不会耽误生产。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 其实，他二人对祁主任也是一无瓜葛二无感情，乐得在一旁看热闹。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们组织了几十个人，在一个假日里带着写好批判政治部祁主任的各种大字报、漫画，还有要祁主任做公开检查的勒令，来到团部。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们将大字报铺天盖地张帖在团部办公大楼显眼的地点，一霎时，引起很多人围观。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在那种政治运动压倒一切的大环境下，谁也不敢为林彪、孔老二在我们团的代理人说话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 何况，我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">充分联系本团“阶级斗争和两条路线斗争实际”，所批判的是“极少数领导干部”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他祁主任“不批林，不批孔，捂盖子，怕群众，甚至采取恶劣手段挑动群众斗群众，破坏革命，破坏生产，煽动经济主义，破坏知识青年上山下乡”，句句都是按中央的指示，联系到祁主任本人的实际言行，有事实，有根据，义正词严。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们在张贴大字报的时候，居然有个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">现役<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">军人在旁边说：“就应该这样斗他！”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可见这个祁主任树敌之多。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大部分军队干部没见过这种阵势，都懵了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 地方干部则在一边幸灾乐祸<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看热闹<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 祁主任躲在家里，不敢露面。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团长和政委来到办公大楼下面，仔细地看起大字报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团长看了一会，笑笑走了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大家都知道，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是一年到头不在团里，只呆在原先的部队里闹着要回去<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。他是个军事干部<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，不想憋屈在生产建设兵团<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">管理农业生产工作<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 政委一直在严肃地<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">仔细<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">地<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看大字报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我对政委很熟悉，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他姓谢，叫谢金源。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他原先在我的家乡六安独立营任教导营政委，因为我是六安人，我们谈过几次家常，彼此印象都不错。我走到谢政委身边，要求他转告祁主任，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们革命群众在等待他觉悟，等待他做深刻检查。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委客气地对我说，小甄同志，不要一棍子把人打死嘛。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我说，没有没有，我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">按照党的治病救人方针，是在挽救他，我们欢迎他回到毛主席的革命路线上来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委只能苦笑。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我要求谢政委派人看护大字报，谢政委答应也是，不答应也不是，一直跟我顾左右言他。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我也没有再难为谢政委，在团部折腾了近两个小时，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">锉<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">掉<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">锐气的目的已经达到。此时，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们一大阵人方嘻嘻哈转回连部。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 且看<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">如何应对，如何动作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">任何<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">应对，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有任何动作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 祁主任后来没有做检查，也没再上班，他病了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五大三粗，貌似凶狠的祁主任，骨子里身体<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和精神<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竟然<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很虚弱<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他不但病了，还病得不轻。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他不是装病，据说他有很多病。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 至此，他就卧床不起几个月<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">先<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在团部医院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗，后转院到天长县医院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗，最<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">后<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竟然转院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">到上海<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">去<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一直没有出院。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这一次“批林批孔”运动，我们巧妙地将一场政治阴谋的斗争，转换为工人维权斗争。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过这件事情，改变了军人居高临下、盛气凌人的工作作风。最大的胜利，是团党委决定星期天按<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">国家<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">规定放假。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大圹圩农场的工人，为争取执行法定假<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">持续<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十年的维权斗争，终于得以实现。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委知道我和副<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">政委<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">岳中林关系特殊，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也知道我救过周副团长，知道周副团长对我十分欣赏。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">因此<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，谢政委对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我一直保持着表面的友善。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过这件事情，他开始对我戒备，我对他则更加敬而远之。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这年，我被选为九团农业学大寨积极分子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，得到了团党委的嘉奖<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我被选为九团农业学大寨积极分子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的实际意义，是使有些人想把我打成阶级敌人的愿望，化为泡影。<br />\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-16 20:52","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-16 20:52:41","ShortDate":"07-16 20:52","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":391,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_393_0\"><font size=\"5\">咋的啦，总也出不来？<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u18611132/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-17 12:49","online":true,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-17 12:49:47","ShortDate":"07-17 12:49","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u18611132.htm","UserID":18611132,"UserName":"陈年老卤","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":392,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_394_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">七十，炮打祁主任<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们之所以<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">瞄上<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">政治部祁主任，并不是仅仅因为他在放电影风波中想将我打成阶级敌人，我的气量还不至于这么狭窄。这里面，有好几个原因。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一是此人对下极其凶狠，声言兵团战士要“轻伤不下火线”，不是大病就必须下地干活。他命令医院和各连卫生室，对病号“发烧不到三十九度的，不许开病假条”。他在兵团战士<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的心中，人人痛恨。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二是此人在军人中亦口碑不佳，遭人嫉恨。团部许多老资格的军队干部，都说他是坐“直升飞机”升上来的，对他多是笑脸相迎，侧目而视。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三是此人一贯高高在上，目中无人。他从不下连队，更看不起地方干部。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">同事中没人缘，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">群众中没基础。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 四是此人阶级斗争观念极强，最喜欢对别人上纲上线，无论发生什么事，他都喜欢草木皆兵，都要往阶级斗争新动向上扯。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这次我们借“批林批孔”运动，正好可以“以其人之道，反制其人之身”，还以颜色。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五是我们要向团党委提出要求，星期天和法定假，应该按国家规定执行放假。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大圹圩农场自成立那天起，就是每月只放一天假。这本身是违法的，工人为此抗争多年，奈何<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">权大于法，掌权的人对此一合理要求不予理睬<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">基层民众<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">手中无权<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">无选票<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，只能任人摆布。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在这时候提出落实法定假，一定会深得人心。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我估计，将矛头对准祁主任个人，不是对着团政治部，团党委就不会为他个人被批判而为他说话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们也做好了准备，如果团党委要出头为祁主任说话，那我们就连团党委一起炮轰。届时，我们将认定团党委是我们团“林彪、孔老二”代理人的保护伞，让团党委引火烧身。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谁敢反对我们无产阶级“批林批孔”？谁敢反对我们保卫毛主席？谁敢反对我们保卫无产阶级文化大革命的旗手江青？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们就铁了心要跟毛主席干革命了，谁怕谁啊？<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-17 16:43","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-17 16:43:28","ShortDate":"07-17 16:43","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":393,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_395_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 回到三连，我们在大会上传达了省兵团有关“批林批孔”的文件<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会后<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">开始发动群众，准备材料，写好充足的炮打政治部祁主任大字报以备用。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 那些新<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一听说我们要炮打政治部祁主任，一个个心里乐开花。他们摩拳擦掌，欢欣鼓舞。在学校，他们还小，没赶上能亲自上阵斗人，没想到下放到兵团了，还能遇到这样新鲜的事情。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗指导员和赵连长也被连续不断的政治运动弄晕了，对我们的行动，有些无所适从<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，也有些担心<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。无所适从<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，是不知道上面到底要做什么。担心，是怕耽误生产。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我劝他俩别担心，我向他们保证，“批林批孔”批祁主任，不会耽误生产。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 其实，他二人对祁主任也是一无瓜葛二无感情，乐得在一旁看热闹。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们组织了几十个人，在一个假日里带着写好批判政治部祁主任的各种大字报、漫画，还有要祁主任做公开检查的勒令，来到团部。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们将大字报铺天盖地张帖在团部办公大楼显眼的地点，一霎时，引起很多人围观。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在那种政治运动压倒一切的大环境下，谁也不敢为林彪、孔老二在我们团的代理人说话。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 何况，我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">充分联系本团“阶级斗争和两条路线斗争实际”，所批判的是“极少数领导干部”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他祁主任“不批林，不批孔，捂盖子，怕群众，甚至采取恶劣手段挑动群众斗群众，破坏革命，破坏生产，煽动经济主义，破坏知识青年上山下乡”，句句都是按中央的指示，联系到祁主任本人的实际言行，有事实，有根据，义正词严。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们在张贴大字报的时候，居然有个<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">现役<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">军人在旁边说：“就应该这样斗他！”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可见这个祁主任树敌之多。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大部分军队干部没见过这种阵势，都懵了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 地方干部则在一边幸灾乐祸<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看热闹<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 祁主任躲在家里，不敢露面。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团长和政委来到办公大楼下面，仔细地看起大字报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 团长看了一会，笑笑走了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大家都知道，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">团长<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是一年到头不在团里，只呆在原先的部队里闹着要回去<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。他是个军事干部<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，不想憋屈在生产建设兵团<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">管理农业生产工作<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 政委一直在严肃地<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">仔细<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">地<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">看大字报。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我对政委很熟悉，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他姓谢，叫谢金源。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他原先在我的家乡六安独立营任教导营政委，因为我是六安人，我们谈过几次家常，彼此印象都不错。我走到谢政委身边，要求他转告祁主任，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们革命群众在等待他觉悟，等待他做深刻检查。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委客气地对我说，小甄同志，不要一棍子把人打死嘛。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我说，没有没有，我们<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">按照党的治病救人方针，是在挽救他，我们欢迎他回到毛主席的革命路线上来。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委只能苦笑。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我要求谢政委派人看护大字报，谢政委答应也是，不答应也不是，一直跟我顾左右言他。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我也没有再难为谢政委，在团部折腾了近两个小时，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">锉<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">掉<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">锐气的目的已经达到。此时，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我们一大阵人方嘻嘻哈转回连部。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 且看<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">如何应对，如何动作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 但<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">祁主任<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">任何<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">应对，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">没有任何动作。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 祁主任后来没有做检查，也没再上班，他病了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 五大三粗，貌似凶狠的祁主任，骨子里身体<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和精神<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竟然<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">很虚弱<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他不但病了，还病得不轻。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他不是装病，据说他有很多病。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 至此，他就卧床不起几个月<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">先<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">在团部医院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗，后转院到天长县医院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗，最<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">后<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">竟然转院<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">到上海<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">去<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">住院<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">治疗。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一直没有出院。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这一次“批林批孔”运动，我们巧妙地将一场政治阴谋的斗争，转换为工人维权斗争。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过这件事情，改变了军人居高临下、盛气凌人的工作作风。最大的胜利，是团党委决定星期天按<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">国家<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">规定放假。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大圹圩农场的工人，为争取执行法定假<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">持续<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十年的维权斗争，终于得以实现。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 谢政委知道我和副<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">政委<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">岳中林关系特殊，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也知道我救过周副团长，知道周副团长对我十分欣赏。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">因此<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，谢政委对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我一直保持着表面的友善。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经过这件事情，他开始对我戒备，我对他则更加敬而远之。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这年，我被选为九团农业学大寨积极分子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，得到了团党委的嘉奖<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我被选为九团农业学大寨积极分子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的实际意义，是使有些人想把我打成阶级敌人的愿望，化为泡影。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u28748671/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">一生钟爱诗书画<br>\r\n半世消磨烟酒茶<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"15-07-17 16:46","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2015-07-17 16:46:59","ShortDate":"07-17 16:46","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d214637218.u28748671.htm","UserID":28748671,"UserName":"半醉汉","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":394,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"2015-07-31 17:38:48","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_396_0\"><font size=\"6\">为何不放行？请小编给个理由！<\/font><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td c