_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_398_0\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\">七十一，故人零落书剑荒<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;font-weight:bold;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一九七四年秋，全国各地工业生产开始复苏。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们安徽省淮北煤矿为扩大生产，派员到我们九团来招调煤矿工人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这次商调的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">条件很宽松，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">一大批一九六四年到大圹圩农场的单身老知青，都报名去了淮北煤矿。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大家都知道，到煤矿就是在矿井下干挖煤工作，既累又危险<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，但收入可观<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 兵团的工作是露天种庄稼，既劳累，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">收入又低<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">风里来雨里去，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">与农民无二。所以他们宁愿选择到危险的煤矿去井下挖煤，也不愿意在建设兵团种地。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们三连这次一下调走好几十<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">名<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老知青，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">他们都是<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">和我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">都是一起下放<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十年<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">的难兄难弟<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">虽然有的不是老乡，但都<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">同甘共苦的好兄弟。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我向我们连没走的老知青提议，每人出五块钱，请所有调走的老知青在一起会餐一顿<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，为他们隆重<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">饯别<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此一建议<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，得到大家<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">热情由衷地<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">支持。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们开始准备这顿“最后的晚餐”。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不料我的建议被文革<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">运动中<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">来的新知青知道后，他们很<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">有想法<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">向我提出请求，说他们<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">也要出钱参加这次饯别。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 他们说<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，你们这些文革前<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">老知青<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">对<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们帮助很大，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">与我们这些新知青<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">是亦师亦友的关系。今师友调走，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">们一定要<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">出钱<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">参加<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这次<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">饯别<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">会餐<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 盛情难却，我只好答应。&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 于是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，原计划的不足百人的饯别，变成了一百好几十人。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 没有那么大吃饭的场地，我们将仓库腾开<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">当会餐地点<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。没有那么多桌子，将已婚老知青家里的大门下<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">下<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">掉<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">搬来，垫在笆斗箩筐上当桌子。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们买酒卖肉，<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">借食堂的锅灶，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">自己做饭做菜，到各家各户借碗借盆<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">借板凳<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当晚，我们新老知青一百多人聚集在一起，在几盏煤油灯下开怀畅饮，祝愿调走的弟兄们能从此改变命运。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 席间，大家谈笑风生，依依惜别，说不尽的话短情长。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 十年啊，十年缺衣少食的患难，十年面朝黄土背朝天、雨打风吹的青春消耗，就这样一无所有、孑然一身而苍凉离别。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不知谁高声长吟了一句：“十年生死两茫茫，不思量，自难忘。千里孤坟，无处话凄凉。纵使相逢应不识，尘满面，鬓如霜。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 压抑、苦闷、潜伏在心底的悲怆，终于被苏轼<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">这阕《<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">江城子<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">》的缠绵悱恻，凄凉地<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">掀开<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">了<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 调走的老知青中有人抽泣，有人大哭，还有人痛哭呼喊：“我不想走了啊！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">我<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">不<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">想<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">走了<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">啊<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，我<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">就<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">死在这里算了。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 更有甚者，有一个新知青在痛哭：“我不想活了，真不想活了。”<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此情此景，令人心碎。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大部分人都喝醉了。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我也很伤感。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 回眸飘零在<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">大<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">圹圩的十年，工作生活，不堪重负。政治高压，如履薄冰。国家大事，混乱不堪。个人奋斗，一事无成<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">以<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">说是<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">十年凄苦，青春空耗<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">，书剑俱荒。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 原本他乡漂流，今又故人零落。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 悲夫！<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:18pt;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"